property.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED- BEST AND FINAL OFFERS ARE DUE TUESDAY, 11/11 BY 12 NOON. Enjoy this charming Collingswood home with beautiful Cooper River views.  This meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on a quiet dead-end street, is just steps from Cooper River Park and a short walk to downtown Collingswood. Some features include an updated kitchen with stainless appliances, refinished hardwood floors, original millwork, solid wood doors, gas fireplace, full basement and an enclosed front porch. Detached 2 car garage with opener, new large Trex deck and a private landscaped yard make for the perfect outdoor entertaining space. Easy access to PATCO, bridges, shops, and parks. Walk to the Avenue where you will delight in delicious restaurants, boutiques, a farmers market and street festivals. Cooper River is at your fingertips where you can enjoy sailing, kayaking, walking trails and more just across the street. This one has it all!
